These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, davidoff, game, oliveros
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Cigar   | game | davidoff | ritmeester | oliveros |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
City: hannover, new-york, boston, berlin
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| City   | hannover | boston | new-york | berlin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, mirinda, tea, juice
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | tea | soy-milk | mirinda | juice |

