1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | november | october | april | march |

